node.text:
to celebrate the launch of @glamnetic x LILHUDDY, 2 winners will win a full pr package signed by yours truly !! 
TO ENTER:
follow @glamnetic + @lilhuddy 
like & save this post
tag a friend (1 comment = 1 entry)

BONUS ENTRIES:
repost this to your IG Stories and tag @glamnetic and @lilhuddy 
comment your favorite style from the collection 

this is a giveaway you don’t want to miss !! good luck 🤘🏻
#GlamneticxLILHUDDY
 no purchase required to enter !

node.text:
i am so damn excited to finally announce my @glamnetic x LILHUDDY collab, bringing you 10 different nail sets and styles that I handpicked and designed myself. with a brand new technology of gel nail stickers, you can do your nails in three short steps: stick, file, and cure! i am so excited to get to share this project with you all, and i can’t wait to see how you all express yourself with them - the possibilities are literally endless!

#GlamneticxLILHUDDY launches on 8.19.21 @ 10 AM PST

node.text:
and finally, my third and final announcement this week… my debut album “Teenage Heartbreak” is out SEPTEMBER 17TH
words can’t even describe how excited I am to share this fucking masterpiece with the world i have never been this proud of an accomplishment of mine before and i know y’all will be proud too. my new song from the album Don’t Freak Out feat. @ianndior, @tysonritter, and @travisbarker is out rn go stream! the official music video is out tomorrow at 9am pt LETS RAGGGEEEE
